## Data & Libraries

### Libraries

```{r}
#| message: false
#| warning: false

library(tidyverse)    # data manipulation and visualization
library(leaflet)      # interactive maps
library(sf)           # spatial operations
library(knitr)        # table formatting
library(kableExtra)   # enhanced tables
library(scales)       # number formatting
library(ggplot2)      # static charts
```

### Data Sources

This project uses two primary datasets:

- **MTA Subway Stations** (`MTA_Subway_Stations.csv`): Station-level data from the MTA Open Data portal including ADA status, borough, routes, and coordinates.
- **NYC PLUTO** (`PLUTO_filtered_near_inaccessible_stations.csv`): A pre-filtered subset of NYC's Primary Land Use Tax Lot Output dataset, containing only high-density zoning parcels within \~500 meters of an inaccessible subway station. Full dataset available at [NYC Open Data](https://data.cityofnewyork.us/).

```{r}
#| message: false

# Load MTA station data
mta <- read_csv("MTA_Subway_Stations.csv")

# Load filtered PLUTO data
pluto <- read_csv("PLUTO_filtered_near_inaccessible_stations.csv")

# Preview
glimpse(mta)
```

### Data Transformation

```{r}
# Recode ADA status to readable labels
mta <- mta %>%
  mutate(
    ada_status = case_when(
      ADA == 1 ~ "Fully Accessible",
      ADA == 2 ~ "Partially Accessible",
      ADA == 0 ~ "Not Accessible"
    ),
    ada_status = factor(ada_status, levels = c("Fully Accessible", 
                                                "Partially Accessible", 
                                                "Not Accessible")),
    # Recode borough abbreviations
    borough_full = case_when(
      Borough == "M"  ~ "Manhattan",
      Borough == "Bk" ~ "Brooklyn",
      Borough == "Q"  ~ "Queens",
      Borough == "Bx" ~ "Bronx",
      Borough == "SI" ~ "Staten Island"
    )
  )

# Separate inaccessible stations
inaccessible <- mta %>% filter(ADA == 0)

cat("Total stations:", nrow(mta), "\n")
cat("Inaccessible stations:", nrow(inaccessible), "\n")
cat("Fully accessible stations:", sum(mta$ADA == 1), "\n")
```

